"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前用ipod classic都仲會經電腦入歌<br />\n依家直接用spotify聽算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買碟係用黎收藏同表示支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣都係買黎支持同收藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dad40bdd07cd43c47fa3cd1245590b23e21059e","tid":50794,"uid":16511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Rip完都冇24bit <br />\nDigital version仲可能有24</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要去hires網買<br />\n最弊係啲撚頭會share出嚟，搞到呢類市場唔會蓬勃，反觀日本就發展得好好多<br />\n而且香港公司嗰啲，以佢哋嘅品德你都要懷疑下係咪真係hires檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁日本既hi res上網仲易搵到<br />\n一樣買碟支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買完只會同D 會買正版CD 既FD SHARE ...<br />\n<br />\nD 唔買碟既問我都唔會俾佢...<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ykk4N.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkk4N.gif&h=ddeb3c12&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ykk4N.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkk4N.gif&h=ddeb3c12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"795db9d5e499ae35decb2df43093f2cbb1c2f60b","tid":50794,"uid":39889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家d cd 點放？我淨係疊埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有部份放左入箱<br />\n仲有廿零三十隻冇位堆左係台頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n為左擺啲cd突登搭左個櫃出黎，逐隻分開擺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過抹塵真係唔可以懶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想好似hmv果d架咁<br />\n但係細細地，整番2/3層擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edb31338b155654b99f44fd712aefb90293e916","tid":50794,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:25:24.000Z","msg":"最近無錢，已經冇買兩年，以前多數rip 無捐放落電話/ mp3/ ipad"},{"pid":"d33ae500e849ef60bc3ddff6840c2b77e900b699","tid":50794,"uid":60814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇教學rip 做flac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔難<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/cdripguide/eac/eac-setup-guide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fsite%2Fcdripguide%2Feac%2Feac-setup-guide&d=q8bVNSdJZRkjnzYTvGcDEAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=0f068b46\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/site/cdripguide/eac/eac-setup-guide</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上裝好eac<br />\n入隻大路碟initial verify你個cd rom drive<br />\n入埋條script嚟較好flac個壓縮度<br />\n<br />\nrip個時就detect gap先<br />\ngen番個m3u嚟做player list<br />\n之後test &amp; rip咁出到嚟就準<br />\n同埋有舊log check到隻碟啲detail<br />\n<br />\n啲private tracker同鬼佬交換碟<br />\n係要咁rip先至受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外有時都同下巴打咁share碟<br />\n全盛時期rip左成二百隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n玩eac轉咗wav+cue仲好<br />\n永久保存隻碟<br />\n有需要就mount再轉做乜檔都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用開flac都係貪佢細過wav同有tag<br />\n反正lossless轉lossless冇咩所謂<br />\n<br />\n係有啲盲毛走去mp3轉lossless咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd031050ff8afb59144be62ba0380c75012cefb","tid":50794,"uid":60814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家d cd 點放？我淨係疊埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有部份放左入箱<br />\n仲有廿零三十隻冇位堆左係台頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n為左擺啲cd突登搭左個櫃出黎，逐隻分開擺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過抹塵真係唔可以懶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買左兩個ikea個cd櫃放<br />\n不過都開始擺唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879d87888132f7117048fc1daa66ce09fbfdce92","tid":50794,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T01:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家d cd 點放？我淨係疊埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有部份放左入箱<br />\n仲有廿零三十隻冇位堆左係台頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n為左擺啲cd突登搭左個櫃出黎，逐隻分開擺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過抹塵真係唔可以懶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買左兩個ikea個cd櫃放<br />\n不過都開始擺唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長型黑色嗰隻?幾好可以併埋好多個"},{"pid":"275ccb72539419993c5ca7f159eeb1c74096791f","tid":50794,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T01:26:21.000Z","msg":"CD嘅好處唔係下載比到，唔同國家印嘅入面啲嘢唔相同，例如呢隻日本版嘅Bon Jovi CD有英日文歌詞紙對照，行CD舖係樂趣嚟，可以尋寶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/0